.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
Birthday: december, august
Sport: skiing, volleyball
1. Birthday:august is in an odd position##4
2. Sport:skiing is on the left or right of Birthday:december##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Birthday   | august | december   |
| Sport         | skiing | volleyball |

